\s Univute, Yesu, nifuate nyayo zako
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Univute, \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd , nifuate nyayo zako, ’kiwa kwa rafiki au katika wageni, na mahali pa furaha au sikitiko; sina budi kumkaribia \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd . \bd*
\pc \bdit Nimfuate, nimkaribie, siku zote na popote nimwandame \bdit*\bdit Yesu\bdit*\bdit ! Nimfuate, nimkaribie, \bdit*\bdit Yesu\bdit*\bdit  mbele, nami nyuma, hata mwisho! \bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Juu ya milima nitasikiliza \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd , hata mabondeni nitaandamana naye. Jua, giza, afya, ’gonjwa, utulivu, vita, kati’ hayo yote \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd  yu karibu. \bd*
\pc \bdit Nimfuate, nimkaribie, siku zote na popote nimwandame \bdit*\bdit Yesu\bdit*\bdit ! Nimfuate, nimkaribie, \bdit*\bdit Yesu\bdit*\bdit  mbele, nami nyuma, hata mwisho! \bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Nikiteka maji, au nikilima shamba, nikika’ nyumbani au ’kiwa safarini, hata huko soko neno moja ni halisi: Sina budi kumkaribia \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd . \bd*
\pc \bdit Nimfuate, nimkaribie, siku zote na popote nimwandame \bdit*\bdit Yesu\bdit*\bdit ! Nimfuate, nimkaribie, \bdit*\bdit Yesu\bdit*\bdit  mbele, nami nyuma, hata mwisho! \bdit*
